**Design:** Descriptive, combining quantitative (survey) and qualitative (open-ended) methods.
**Data Collection:**
- Structured questionnaire to 500 randomly selected residents
- Topics: housing prices, availability, socio-economic status, urban development perception

**Analysis Tools:**
- Descriptive stats (percentages)
- Inferential stats: Chi-Square (availability), Regression (price impact)
- Software: R with bar/pie charts for visual output
